rComments: She is very laid back and is willing to teach you French if you're actually interested in learning the language. If you just need to complete your minor you can still get an easy A. Just pay attention to the assignment parameters and participate.

She teaches at University of Louisiana at Lafayette. She sometimes seems a little lost and is hard to communicate with in English sometimes (but it is her 3rd language so I will cut her some slack). We didn't have hardly any grades all year until the second to last week where she dumped three huge assignments on us. Kind of frustrating.
